This package is a port of individual tree segmentation (ITS) algorithms from
the R package `lidR` (https://github.com/r-lidar/lidR), licensed under
GPL-3.0-or-later. Algorithm correctness and parameter semantics follow lidR
v4.3.2; see docs/specs/2026-04-30-pylidar-its-design.md for the migration
mapping.


Third-Party Components
