Build-time Dependencies (not redistributed in the wheel source)
---------------------------------------------------------------

* nanobind (https://github.com/wjakob/nanobind, BSD-3-Clause) — Python C++
  binding generator. Pulled in via `pyproject.toml [build-system].requires`;
  produces the `_core` extension module shipped in the wheel.

* scikit-build-core (https://github.com/scikit-build/scikit-build-core,
  Apache-2.0) — PEP 517 build backend.

These tools are used to build pylidar but their source is not redistributed
inside pylidar wheels.
